    <h1>Privacy Policy</h1>
    <p><strong>Effective Date:</strong> 30/11/2024</p>
    <p>Thank you for choosing MastaKash, your trusted partner in Chama and group management. This Privacy Policy explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information when you use our application. By accessing our app, you agree to the practices described in this policy.</p>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
        <p>To provide effective group management services, we may collect the following information:</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>1.1 Personal Information:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Name</li>
                    <li>Contact details (email address, phone number)</li>
                    <li>Basic identification data, if required for user verification</li>
                    <li>Profile pictures or photos uploaded voluntarily by users</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>1.2 Group Information:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Group names, member lists, and associated details for effective Chama or group management</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>1.3 App Usage Data:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Information on app interactions and features accessed to improve functionality</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
        <p>We use the information collected to enhance your experience with MastaKash and provide administrative support for your group activities.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>2.1 Deliver and Improve Services:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Enable Chama-related functionalities such as member management, activity scheduling, and reporting</li>
                    <li>Facilitate seamless communication within groups</li>
                    <li>Customize the app interface and features based on user preferences</li>
                    <li>Provide customer support and respond to inquiries</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
            <li><strong>2.2 Compliance and Security:</strong>
                <ul>
                    <li>Maintain the integrity and security of group data</li>
                    <li>Prevent unauthorized access or misuse of the app</li>
                    <li>Address any legal or regulatory requirements</li>
                </ul>
            </li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>3. Information Sharing</h2>
        <p>Your privacy is important to us, and we ensure your information is handled responsibly.</p>
        <ul>
            <li><strong>3.1 Service Providers:</strong> We may share information with trusted third-party service providers who assist in delivering app services (e.g., cloud hosting or analytics). These providers are bound by confidentiality agreements.</li>
            <li><strong>3.2 Legal and Regulatory Requirements:</strong> We may disclose information if required by law or to respond to valid legal processes.</li>
            <li><strong>3.3 Group Members:</strong> Certain information, such as group details or member contributions, may be visible to group participants for administrative purposes.</li>
        </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>4. Data Security</h2>
        <p>We take reasonable steps to protect your information against unauthorized access, loss, or misuse. Security measures include encryption and regular audits. However, no system is entirely secure, and we encourage you to take precautions to safeguard your login credentials.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>5. Your Rights</h2>
        <p>You have the right to:</p>
        <ul>
            <li>Access: Request details of the personal information we hold about you</li>
            <li>Correction: Update or correct inaccuracies in your information</li>
            <li>Deletion: Request the removal of your personal information where applicable</li>
            <li>Withdrawal of Consent: Revoke consent for specific uses of your data</li>
        </ul>
        <p>For assistance with these rights, contact us using the details in the "Contact Us" section below.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>6. Updates to the Privacy Policy</h2>
        <p>We may update this Privacy Policy periodically to reflect changes in the app or legal requirements. Updates will be posted within the app, and we encourage you to review the policy regularly.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
        <h2>7. Contact Us</h2>
